English, English

00:13.951 --> 00:15.265
learn english!

00:15.385 --> 00:18.374
My three-year-old nephew
can speak it and he's an idiot.

00:18.496 --> 00:19.770
How hard can it be?

00:19.890 --> 00:21.668
Set traps on your way out.

00:21.865 --> 00:23.095
Set traps.

00:23.133 --> 00:24.739
Senor Bennie, no me gustan la trampas.

00:24.759 --> 00:26.852
- You don't like traps.
- Podrian matar a alguien.

00:26.872 --> 00:29.177
Of course it can kill someone.
That's the whole point.

00:29.297 --> 00:31.904
If somebody breaks in here,
somebody tries to rob from me,

00:32.024 --> 00:33.748
they get what's comin' to 'em!

00:33.985 --> 00:35.358
That's how we do things.

00:35.478 --> 00:37.519
Listen, when you're an American,

00:37.772 --> 00:38.948
you'll understand.

01:17.093 --> 01:17.942
Okay.

01:18.454 --> 01:22.274
Okay, don't do anything stupid.

01:24.124 --> 01:25.608
Not much of a talker?

01:25.696 --> 01:29.215
Don't take another step,
i'm warning you, not one more step.

01:36.827 --> 01:38.447
I tried to tell you.

01:38.948 --> 01:40.723
Nobody listens to me.

